# Data table with reactable


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(reactable)
library(reactablefmtr)
mtcars %>% reactable()%>% 
  # Main title
  reactablefmtr::add_title(
    title = 'Main title'
  ) %>% 
    # sub title
  reactablefmtr::add_subtitle(
    subtitle = 'sub title',
    font_weight = 'normal'
  )
```

